{"tid":1799572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維基百科報料Bot正式上線","createTime":"2019-12-27T05:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T08:01:07.000Z","uid":71237,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba5517292cdf7da702eb6f8b853661b9eae621b","tid":1799572,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"維基百科戰線建立以來，不時我們都會收到求助，指有藍絲破壞頁面、抹黑香港示威者等等。<br />\n為咗更有效率地處理，我們正式推出「維基百科報料Bot」。<br />\n<br />\n大家喺維基百科發現有人惡意破壞（例如將黃之鋒改為已死亡）、無故大量刪除具有可靠來源的內容，或者發現有啲嘢值得寫，都可以透過「報料Bot」通知我地。<br />\n<br />\n然後admin們可能會親自處理，或者經過過濾、整理後由「任務Channel」呼籲其他維基人撰寫。<br />\n而各位維基人喺編輯時遇到困難或者疑問，亦都可以喺去「維基公海Group」發問，admin或者其他維基人會提供協助和解答。<br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線解說：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY1G6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY1G6ad.jpg&h=93cc57c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「報料Bot」有助盡快發現惡意破壞，以及收集值得收錄嘅內容。<br />\n「任務Channel」可以召集有心寫嘢嘅維基人參與條目，讓條目有人處理，同時亦提供機會比新手練習。<br />\n「維基公海Group」可以解答各位編輯時嘅疑問，討論複雜問題，長遠為維基百科戰線培訓更多人才。<br />\n<br />\n報料Bot：收集惡意破壞報告、值得寫嘅內容<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wikiscout_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwikiscout_bot&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=b8a0e2ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wikiscout_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n任務Channel：歡迎你想寫嘢但又唔知有咩可以寫嘅維基人加入。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=79e5a170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2bbed854ea076516bb0132149033737c29ef0b","tid":1799572,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:14:21.000Z","msg":"之前都寫過關於維基百科的新手教學，如果大家有心參與維基百科，請仔細閱讀以下兩個post：<br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n[教學] 如何成為維基百科撰寫師？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"63ad5f2a35105683a567d32b0ca8e78cfc484a07","tid":1799572,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"30d7986ca3328f8826504cebb27c0f830f997405","tid":1799572,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:23:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20dec077054d5160039b188fd3f7daed4e02e571","tid":1799572,"uid":315569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c98baf8c9b3ab971b821bdf031d98acb7bc6146e","tid":1799572,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429290c473da5c93d626ffa66010bd66c9fdfb00","tid":1799572,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"452a6600eeb0a73ee758b594b8b39bc0b9b5b62f","tid":1799572,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8512f3f98e685e70a276127bde0adc95a92a1d","tid":1799572,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"452a6600eeb0a73ee758b594b8b39bc0b9b5b62f","tid":1799572,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"自膠襟錯左不推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\"